{"article_id":"VAGfnjvxL3YXJA99","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President-elect Donald Trump is expected to be briefed Friday on a report","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"prepared by the U.S. intelligence community","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"on Russian hacking activities in the presidential election","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"--","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after he spent this week still questioning the veracity of their previous assessments .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"On Thursday , President Obama received a briefing on the report","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"-- prepared by the CIA , FBI and NSA --","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"which he had ordered in December .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Director of National Intelligence James Clapper said Thursday","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that an unclassified version of the report will be made public early next week .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"In testimony before the Senate Armed Services Committee Thursday , Clapper previewed some of the report ' s findings .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"\" Hacking was only part of it , \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"about Russia ' s cyber activities during the election .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" It also entailed classical propaganda , disinformation , fake news . \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Clapper will be one of four intelligence chiefs","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"to brief Mr. Trump on the report Friday at Trump Tower in New York .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"The other briefers will be CIA Director John Brennan , FBI Director James Comey and National Security Agency Director Adm. Mike Rogers .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"For weeks , the president-elect has been questioning the U.S. intelligence community ' s integrity and its assessment","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"that Russia not only launched cyberattacks against the U.S.","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"to sow doubt in the election ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"but to sway the outcome in favor of Mr. Trump .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Since the final weeks of the campaign , he also doubted","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that Russia was responsible .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Trump claimed on New Year ' s Eve","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that he had information","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"no one else had on Russian hacking","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and that he would reveal it publicly this week ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"but he has not yet followed through on that statement .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"On Wednesday , he posted a tweet","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"indicating","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"he ' s still not convinced","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Russia is to blame for cyberattacks against the Democratic National Committee","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"( DNC ) ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"other political groups and Hillary Clinton ' s campaign chairman John Podesta .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"The `` Intelligence '' briefing on so-called `` Russian hacking '' was delayed until Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"perhaps more time","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"needed","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"to build a case .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Very strange !","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"January 4 , 2017","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"A number of Republicans in Congress like Rep. Michael McCaul , R-Texas , chairman of the Homeland Security Committee , are adamant about the need","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"for the new administration to develop a more clear-cut cyber policy","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and to punish Russia for its actions .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"McCaul expressed confidence in the intelligence Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that the evidence","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"he was briefed on in both classified and unclassified settings","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"\" was very clear , \"","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"and he said","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that it was clear the attacks were \" nation state-based . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"the incoming administration needs to take a strong stance against what has happened , \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Sen. John McCain , R-Arizona , and other Republicans warned at his committee ' s hearing","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that Russia must suffer the consequences .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" Every American should be alarmed by Russia ' s attacks on our nation , \"","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"said McCain .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Later in the day , he told reporters","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that the Trump administration should work with Congress","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"to craft a cyber policy .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"\" We ' ll be glad to work with them ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"but they ' ve got to have a policy and a strategy , \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"as he continued to blast the Obama administration","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"for lacking a plan .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" They ' ve never had one .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"They ' ve reacted to every single attack in a different way .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"It ' s just crazy . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Clapper , Rogers and undersecretary of defense for intelligence , Marcel Lettre , issued a joint statement Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"warning","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that Russia is a \" full-scope cyber actor . \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" We assess","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"that only Russia ' s senior-most officials could have authorized the recent election-focused data thefts and disclosures ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"based of the scope and sensitivity of the targets .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Russia also has used cyber tactics and techniques","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"to seek to influence public opinion across Europe and Eurasia , \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"they said .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" Looking forward , Russian cyber operations will likely target the United States","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"to gather intelligence ,","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"support Russian decision-making ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"conduct influence operations","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to support Russian military and political objectives ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"and prepare the cyber environment for future contingencies . \"","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Last week , the Obama administration announced a new series of sanctions against Russian intelligence agents and entities","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"the U.S. says","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"were responsible for hacks into the DNC and other servers .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"In addition to the targeted sanctions , 35 Russian operatives were expelled from the U.S. in retaliation .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-South Carolina , said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"those actions weren ' t good enough","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and had some advice for the president-elect :","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"\" When you listen to these people","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"[ in the intelligence community , ]","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"you can be skeptical ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"but you have to understand","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"they ' re the best among us . \"","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"what Obama did was throw a pill .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"I ' m ready to throw a rock , \"","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"Graham said .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"\" If we don ' t throw rocks ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"we ' re going to make a huge mistake . \"","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Over the next week , Sen. Ben Cardin , D-Maryland , the top Democrat on the Senate Foreign Relations Committee , plans to roll out legislation","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"containing tougher sanctions against Russia .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"\" That hearing today gave a great boost to sanctions , \"","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"McCain said .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Clapper ' s testimony and Roger ' s testimony this morning helps that process along","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"and resolved any doubts","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"as to what the intelligence part of our government thinks . \"","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Mr. Trump , meanwhile , appeared to side this week with WikiLeaks ' s Julian Assange","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"who again denied","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that their source for hacked emails was not the Russian government .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Julian Assange said","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"`` a 14 year old could have hacked Podesta ''","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"- why was DNC so careless ?","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Also said","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Russians did not give him the info !","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"January 4 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Several lawmakers slammed Mr. Trump","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"for questioning the integrity of the intelligence community .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Sen. Claire McCaskill , D-Missouri , asked Clapper ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"\" Who benefits from a president-elect","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"trashing the intelligence community ? \"","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"there is an important distinction here between healthy skepticism , \"","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"Clapper said ,","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"\" ... I think","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"there ' s a difference between skepticism and disparagement . \"","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wisconsin , had positive , but qualified words for the intelligence community .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"\" I do have faith","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that our men and women in the intelligence community are doing an incredible job ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"sacrificing for our country , \"","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"he told reporters Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"\" but there ' s always room for improvement . \"","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"On the question","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"of whether Russians meddled in the presidential election , though ,","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"Ryan firmly believes the intelligence .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"\" Did the Russians hack us ?","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Yes .","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"Is it right for any country to meddle in our elections ?","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"No , \"","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"he said on \" The Jerry Bader Show . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":186,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":164,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":161,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":151,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":149,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":0,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":153,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":154,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nu